1
00:00:35,439 --> 00:00:37,200
This looks exactly like

2
00:00:37,640 --> 00:00:39,000
the photo Advisor He had.

3
00:00:43,119 --> 00:00:44,719
According to Advisor He,

4
00:00:45,560 --> 00:00:47,840
we should head to the highest Royal Palace
for the Silver Eye.

5
00:00:48,399 --> 00:00:48,960
Right.

6
00:00:49,479 --> 00:00:50,840
After we get inside,

7
00:00:50,840 --> 00:00:52,600
we'll head straight for the highest
Royal Palace.

8
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,399
I bet the Silver Eye

9
00:00:54,719 --> 00:00:56,960
is hidden right inside the King's Bedchamber.

10
00:00:59,560 --> 00:01:00,280
Uncle Min,

11
00:01:00,560 --> 00:01:02,479
how are you holding up? Can you make it?

12
00:01:03,039 --> 00:01:05,640
I... I can make it, of course.

13
00:01:06,280 --> 00:01:07,879
I've already made it this far.

14
00:01:08,439 --> 00:01:09,680
Even if it kills me,

15
00:01:10,439 --> 00:01:12,719
I have to go in and find the Silver Eye.

16
00:01:14,840 --> 00:01:16,200
He Lingla isn't doing well.

17
00:01:16,560 --> 00:01:17,359
Bi Huaqiang,

18
00:01:17,879 --> 00:01:19,920
you stay here with Lingla so she can rest.

19
00:01:20,200 --> 00:01:21,120
We'll go in first.

20
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:21,840
Got it.

21
00:01:22,400 --> 00:01:23,760
N-No way.

22
00:01:24,120 --> 00:01:26,959
I... I need to go up and find the Silver Eye.

23
00:01:27,120 --> 00:01:28,400
Oh, give it a rest.

24
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,879
You're suffering from altitude sickness.

25
00:01:29,879 --> 00:01:31,439
You could die here if you're not careful.

26
00:01:31,959 --> 00:01:32,560
Old Lu!

27
00:01:33,239 --> 00:01:34,159
Old Lu, are you okay?

28
00:01:34,159 --> 00:01:34,959
I...

29
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:36,400
I...

30
00:01:38,719 --> 00:01:40,439
I... I'm just...

31
00:01:40,920 --> 00:01:41,640
going up...

32
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:44,640
See?

33
00:01:45,359 --> 00:01:47,400
You'll die trying to get a free ride.

34
00:02:01,159 --> 00:02:02,000
Are you okay?

35
00:02:19,879 --> 00:02:22,240
This... this statue looks familiar.

36
00:02:23,240 --> 00:02:25,520
Curly hair, deep-set eyes,

37
00:02:25,639 --> 00:02:27,479
high nose bridge, thin lips,

38
00:02:27,919 --> 00:02:30,039
muscular and well-built.

39
00:02:30,120 --> 00:02:32,439
This must be the Haixi Fanxiang style.

40
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:46,400
Look at this.

41
00:02:47,039 --> 00:02:48,280
Every stone pillar

42
00:02:48,639 --> 00:02:50,080
has a similar pattern.

43
00:02:51,879 --> 00:02:53,719
All these circles...

44
00:02:53,759 --> 00:02:55,439
What... what does it mean?

45
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,840
This is probably

46
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,840
their record of the sun.

47
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:08,400
Different forms at different times.

48
00:03:09,280 --> 00:03:11,400
Now isn't the time to chat
about Mengna Valley.

49
00:03:11,439 --> 00:03:13,159
We should be looking for the Silver Eye right now.

50
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,039
Brother Chen,

51
00:03:42,879 --> 00:03:44,479
all the palaces here combined

52
00:03:44,479 --> 00:03:45,800
make a total of nine buildings.

53
00:03:45,800 --> 00:03:47,439
Let's think logically based on the layout.

54
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:50,520
These stone pillars are all carved with the sun.

55
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:51,960
So if we assume the Royal Palace

56
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,319
represents the sun,

57
00:03:53,319 --> 00:03:55,039
the eight palaces in the middle

58
00:03:55,280 --> 00:03:56,960
should correspond to other
celestial bodies.

59
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,080
The question is,

60
00:03:58,080 --> 00:04:01,120
where exactly would the Silver Eye be?

61
00:04:02,120 --> 00:04:03,840
Based on our previous deduction,

62
00:04:04,199 --> 00:04:06,199
it should be in the most prominent place.

63
00:04:06,199 --> 00:04:07,759
And the most prominent place

64
00:04:07,759 --> 00:04:09,120
is definitely the Royal Palace.

65
00:04:09,199 --> 00:04:10,960
Isn't the Royal Palace right here?

66
00:04:11,080 --> 00:04:11,840
Exactly.

67
00:04:12,080 --> 00:04:12,919
Not necessarily.

68
00:04:13,159 --> 00:04:14,319
I think it could be

69
00:04:14,319 --> 00:04:15,800
for the city of Juedabu,

70
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,439
the most highly valued star.

71
00:04:17,680 --> 00:04:18,720
The question is,

72
00:04:19,439 --> 00:04:21,319
which one did they value the most?

73
00:04:22,000 --> 00:04:23,600
I... I was just wondering about something.

74
00:04:23,600 --> 00:04:25,319
You said there... there are nine.

75
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:27,920
I've been counting and only found seven.

76
00:04:28,120 --> 00:04:30,000
Sun, Moon,

77
00:04:30,199 --> 00:04:31,639
Venus, Jupiter, Mercury, Mars, and Saturn.

78
00:04:31,720 --> 00:04:33,920
Then... what are the other two?

79
00:04:33,959 --> 00:04:35,399
The orbits of the sun and the moon

80
00:04:35,399 --> 00:04:37,040
intersect in the zodiac,

81
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,360
creating a north and a south node.

82
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,519
The South Node and North Node.

83
00:04:40,639 --> 00:04:42,439
In the traditional astronomical system,

84
00:04:42,480 --> 00:04:44,319
the point of intersection
during a solar eclipse

85
00:04:44,360 --> 00:04:45,519
is also called Rahu.

86
00:04:46,000 --> 00:04:48,279
It's considered an existence
higher than the sun.

87
00:04:48,800 --> 00:04:49,759
That means

88
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:51,759
the palace corresponding to Rahu

89
00:04:51,920 --> 00:04:53,600
should be higher than this Royal Palace.

90
00:04:53,720 --> 00:04:54,519
I think

91
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,639
it is the most likely place

92
00:04:55,639 --> 00:04:56,920
for the Silver Eye to be kept.

93
00:04:56,920 --> 00:04:58,319
I just don't get it.

94
00:04:58,319 --> 00:04:59,439
After all this talk,

95
00:04:59,439 --> 00:05:02,399
the question is,
which is the Rahu Palace?

96
00:05:02,600 --> 00:05:05,120
When this royal city was first built,

97
00:05:05,879 --> 00:05:08,480
each palace corresponded to
a celestial body.

98
00:05:08,639 --> 00:05:10,720
If we look at this
from the king's perspective...

99
00:05:20,879 --> 00:05:21,560
Over there.

100
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,319
So this really is the dragon
devouring the sun.

101
00:05:59,800 --> 00:06:00,639
Brother Chen.

102
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:04,120
Are you sure this place is Rahu?

103
00:06:05,199 --> 00:06:06,879
From the Royal Palace's observatory,

104
00:06:07,160 --> 00:06:08,920
the eight palaces and the Royal Palace
are arranged

105
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:11,160
according to the traditional
astronomical system,

106
00:06:11,199 --> 00:06:13,079
based on the positions of
the nine celestial bodies.

107
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,839
The Royal Palace corresponds to the sun,

108
00:06:14,879 --> 00:06:17,279
so this place must be Rahu.

109
00:06:20,519 --> 00:06:22,240
What are you doing, Fatty?

110
00:06:26,680 --> 00:06:27,920
You know, in here,

111
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:29,680
every plant and tree in these ruins

112
00:06:29,680 --> 00:06:31,079
needs to be carefully protected.

113
00:06:31,279 --> 00:06:32,439
If you break it,

114
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:35,040
a lifetime's wages couldn't pay for it.

115
00:06:37,759 --> 00:06:39,399
Help, give me a hand here.

116
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:40,279
Let's fix it.

117
00:07:05,160 --> 00:07:05,959
What's this?

118
00:07:19,439 --> 00:07:20,480
Let's check over there.

119
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:10,519
Uncle Min, you said before

120
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:11,680
that the Silver Eye is essentially

121
00:08:11,680 --> 00:08:13,040
a coordinate map, right?

122
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,759
That's right.

123
00:08:15,279 --> 00:08:16,879
Then this must be it.

124
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:18,160
All these pieces...

125
00:08:18,199 --> 00:08:19,680
What on earth is this?

126
00:08:20,120 --> 00:08:24,360
Are you sure this thing is the Silver Eye?

127
00:08:25,519 --> 00:08:26,199
Look.

128
00:08:26,800 --> 00:08:27,959
On these fragments,

129
00:08:28,279 --> 00:08:30,199
there are beasts and deities.

130
00:08:30,480 --> 00:08:32,759
These are all elements representing coordinates.

131
00:08:32,759 --> 00:08:34,200
So what you mean is

132
00:08:34,440 --> 00:08:36,759
these also represent
real geographical locations?

133
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,679
Exactly.

134
00:08:46,679 --> 00:08:49,200
On my map of the Mengna Valley territory,

135
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:51,159
it's explained very clearly.

136
00:08:51,200 --> 00:08:53,799
All the mountains and rivers are labeled

137
00:08:53,799 --> 00:08:57,159
with the names of deities
and sacred beasts.

138
00:08:58,080 --> 00:08:59,200
You two keep going on and on,

139
00:08:59,200 --> 00:09:00,919
you're not thinking of
piecing it together, are you?

140
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,000
Don't just stand there. Let's get to it.

141
00:09:03,919 --> 00:09:04,639
Come on, come on.

142
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,120
What's that sound?

143
00:09:55,200 --> 00:09:56,159
Look over there.

144
00:09:58,399 --> 00:09:59,120
Brother Chen.

145
00:10:00,840 --> 00:10:04,559
It's both an eyeball and coordinates.

146
00:10:07,799 --> 00:10:09,480
There's no mistake about it, Brother Chen.

147
00:10:09,480 --> 00:10:10,840
This is the Silver Eye!

148
00:10:18,519 --> 00:10:20,279
This pattern seems drawn to you.

149
00:10:20,360 --> 00:10:21,360
It follows you wherever you go.

150
00:10:21,440 --> 00:10:22,159
Are you all right?

151
00:10:22,879 --> 00:10:23,600
Godfather!

152
00:10:23,799 --> 00:10:24,840
Godfather, what's wrong?

153
00:10:25,200 --> 00:10:27,879
It's nothing, just my old condition.

154
00:10:28,519 --> 00:10:32,159
My scripture mentioned that

155
00:10:32,720 --> 00:10:34,600
the hierarchy of Mengna Valley,

156
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,159
including the Jueda people,

157
00:10:36,799 --> 00:10:39,200
and the earliest origin
of their eye worship

158
00:10:39,200 --> 00:10:40,840
came from Mengna Valley.

159
00:10:41,039 --> 00:10:44,639
Now, this image can't be wrong.

160
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:46,200
This is what will lead us

161
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:48,159
to Mengna Valley—the Silver Eye!

162
00:10:48,159 --> 00:10:49,080
Miss He.

163
00:10:50,320 --> 00:10:53,399
I'm handing this map over to you now.

164
00:10:53,759 --> 00:10:55,279
Compare it with the Silver Eye,

165
00:10:55,679 --> 00:10:57,039
and we'll see where we should head next.

166
00:10:57,039 --> 00:10:59,000
It'll all be visible, you see.

167
00:11:08,879 --> 00:11:09,960
Old Lu, hurry up!

168
00:11:14,519 --> 00:11:15,679
Godfather, slow down.

169
00:11:17,639 --> 00:11:20,159
Talk about shoddy construction.

170
00:11:20,159 --> 00:11:21,279
The Silver Eye!

171
00:11:21,519 --> 00:11:22,559
These Jueda ruins

172
00:11:22,559 --> 00:11:23,840
are over a thousand years old.

173
00:11:24,360 --> 00:11:25,840
It's a miracle they've survived this long.

174
00:11:25,840 --> 00:11:26,279
This

175
00:11:26,279 --> 00:11:28,200
might also have to do with us
removing the fragment.

176
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:29,679
The main beam collapsed!

177
00:11:29,679 --> 00:11:31,320
What if the roof comes down too?

178
00:11:31,320 --> 00:11:32,320
We can't stay here for long.

179
00:11:32,320 --> 00:11:32,919
Quick, run!

180
00:11:32,919 --> 00:11:33,639
Everyone, get out of here now!

181
00:11:33,639 --> 00:11:34,200
We can't leave!

182
00:11:34,200 --> 00:11:36,039
We have to find the Silver Eye.

183
00:11:36,039 --> 00:11:37,559
Godfather, listen to Brother Chen.

184
00:11:37,559 --> 00:11:39,440
Let's get to safety first and talk later.

185
00:11:39,440 --> 00:11:40,320
Anxiang.

186
00:11:40,320 --> 00:11:41,360
Just listen to me.

187
00:11:43,399 --> 00:11:44,200
Look out!

188
00:11:45,559 --> 00:11:46,240
Godfather!

189
00:11:47,200 --> 00:11:48,519
My Silver Eye! Godfather!

190
00:11:48,519 --> 00:11:50,080
What happened? Are you okay?

191
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:51,679
Beneath this Rahu Hall,

192
00:11:52,039 --> 00:11:53,799
there's a cave this deep?

193
00:11:54,679 --> 00:11:56,480
There were indeed records before

194
00:11:56,480 --> 00:11:57,639
that a foreigner

195
00:11:57,960 --> 00:12:00,000
discovered many caves in these ruins.

196
00:12:00,279 --> 00:12:01,279
The most famous among them

197
00:12:01,279 --> 00:12:02,639
is the Headless Mummy Cave.

198
00:12:03,000 --> 00:12:04,080
There's also a weapons cave

199
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,559
filled with a huge amount of weapons.

200
00:12:05,960 --> 00:12:08,039
But they're all far from this Rahu Hall.

201
00:12:08,440 --> 00:12:09,720
What's that thing? It's pitch black.

202
00:12:10,320 --> 00:12:11,519
Look, look, look!

203
00:12:14,559 --> 00:12:17,120
This must be the golden statue
of the Silver Eye.

204
00:12:18,200 --> 00:12:19,279
The Hell's Calamity Mural.

205
00:12:20,080 --> 00:12:22,000
We've really found something good this time.

206
00:12:22,440 --> 00:12:24,080
Forget the murals for a moment.

207
00:12:24,279 --> 00:12:25,519
Just this statue alone,

208
00:12:26,679 --> 00:12:30,120
made of five fused metals,
cast in one piece.

209
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,440
Even with today's craftsmanship,

210
00:12:31,600 --> 00:12:32,799
no one could replicate it.

211
00:12:32,879 --> 00:12:34,879
All right, everyone get out of here, quick.

212
00:12:35,080 --> 00:12:36,519
Right, right, before the roof collapses.

213
00:12:36,519 --> 00:12:37,480
Let's go, let's go, Old Lu!

214
00:12:38,039 --> 00:12:39,440
My Silver Eye!

215
00:12:39,440 --> 00:12:41,720
A Zhong, my cane and gloves,

216
00:12:41,720 --> 00:12:43,279
bring them to me!

